growth_protocol_ch1: Samples are radical prostatectomy tissues directly taken from the patient
extract_protocol_ch1: The standard protocol from RNA-Bee (Campro Scientific) was used to extract total RNA
label_protocol_ch1: Standard whole transcript labeling protocol from Affymetrix human exon 1.0 ST
hyb_protocol: Standard hybridization protocol for Affymetrix human exon 1.0 ST
scan_protocol: Standard scanner for Affymetrix human exon 1.0 ST
data_processing: Cel files were processed using Partek RMA core probeset level
